PrecisAppointment of RICHARD BELLIVEAU as Ambassador of Canada to the People's Democratic Republic of Algeria; JACQUES BILODEAU as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Belgium; ROBERT COLLETTE as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of the Philippines; LOUIS HAMEL as Ambassador and Permanent Delegate of Canada to the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization; MARGARET HUBER as Ambassador of Canada to the Czech Republic; MELVYN MacDONALD as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia with concurrent accreditation to the State of Bahrain, the Sultanate of Oman and the Republic of Yemen; MICHEL PERRAULT as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Cameroon with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Chad; FRANCO PILLARELLA as Ambassador of Canada to the Syrian Arab Republic with concurrent accreditation as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Cyprus; LOUIS POISSON as Ambassador of Canada to the Gabonese Republic; ALLAN S. POOLE as Consul General of Canada at Dallas (United States of America); ASTRID PREGEL as Consul General of Canada at Atlanta (United States of America); EVELYN PUXLEY as Deputy Permanent Representative and Ambassador of Canada to the Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe; COLIN ROBERTSON as Consul General of Canada at Los Angeles (United States of America); SANDELLE SCRIMSHAW as High Commissioner for Canada in Barbados with concurrent accreditation to the Commonwealth of Dominica, Antigua and Barbuda, St. Lucia, the Federation of St. Christopher and Nevis, St. Vincent and the Grenadines; and MICHAEL SMALL as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Cuba.
